fields.description:
Links to some of the Project Administration actions such as "Crucible Settings", "Fisheye Content" and "Operations" are pushed out of the screen on certain screen resolutions such as 1024x768, making them inaccessible for projects with long project names.
As a workaround, the direct URL can be used to access these links, such as for "Crucible Settings -> Edit" link for a certain project, the following URL can be used:
{quote}
http://<Base URL>/admin/viewFisheyeProject.do?id=<Project-ID>
{quote}
Project-ID can be found from the Crucible database under the CRU_PROJECT table:
{quote}
select CRU_PROJECT_ID from CRU_PROJECT where CRU_NAME = '<Affected Project Name>';
{quote}
It does not affect higher resolutions such as 1920x1200 or 1600x1200

Reproduced on IE, FireFox and Safari
